{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/444/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"background-と-opacity-を分けるとうまくいかない\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#background-%E3%81%A8-opacity-%E3%82%92%E5%88%86%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B%E3%81%A8%E3%81%86%E3%81%BE%E3%81%8F%E3%81%84%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84\" aria-label=\"background と opacity を分けるとうまくいかない permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>background と opacity を分けるとうまくいかない</h2>\n<p>ここによくあるボタンのデザインがあります。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 208px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2b48c011012f8eedd4c942b19219d0a7/8f2fb/image-19.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/2b48c011012f8eedd4c942b19219d0a7/8f2fb/image-19.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2b48c011012f8eedd4c942b19219d0a7/8a4e8/image-19.png 150w,\n/static/2b48c011012f8eedd4c942b19219d0a7/8f2fb/image-19.png 208w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 208px) 100vw, 208px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>CSS を設定するために数値を見てみます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 269px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a4374b7fea7dd4b08ff9b873966ac1f8/98fe2/image-24.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/a4374b7fea7dd4b08ff9b873966ac1f8/98fe2/image-24.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a4374b7fea7dd4b08ff9b873966ac1f8/8a4e8/image-24.png 150w,\n/static/a4374b7fea7dd4b08ff9b873966ac1f8/98fe2/image-24.png 269w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 269px) 100vw, 269px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Hex：#E9952C</code>。そして</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 284px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/445bd0f1ea791deff054bde2d8772437/62f93/image-21.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/445bd0f1ea791deff054bde2d8772437/62f93/image-21.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/445bd0f1ea791deff054bde2d8772437/8a4e8/image-21.png 150w,\n/static/445bd0f1ea791deff054bde2d8772437/62f93/image-21.png 284w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">不透明度：80%</code></p>\n<p>もしもこの 2 種類のプロパティを素直にかいた場合、下記のようになるかもしれません。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#E9952C\n<span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>0.8</code></pre></div>\n<p>しかしこれではテキストも透過されてしまうので、カラーコードに対して透過を設定しないといけません。</p>\n<h2 id=\"16進数hexで設定する\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#16%E9%80%B2%E6%95%B0hex%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"16進数hexで設定する permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>16進数(Hex)で設定する</h2>\n<p>デザインソフトでは Hex 値が 6 桁表示になっていますが、8 桁で設定することができます。\n8 桁にすると下二桁は透明度を指します。\nアルファ値の数値はこちらが参考になります。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://qiita.com/CUTBOSS/items/6166cf79b9f18c45a010\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://qiita.com/CUTBOSS/items/6166cf79b9f18c45a010</a></p>\n<p>つまり<code class=\"language-text\">#E9952C</code>と<code class=\"language-text\">透明度80%</code>は、<code class=\"language-text\">#E9952C+CC</code>となるので、CSSはこのように設定します。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#E9952CCC</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"rgbaで設定する\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rgba%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"rgbaで設定する permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>rgbaで設定する</h2>\n<p>rgba の場合はデザインソフトで rgb で表示するように切り替えます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 258px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9e4fe4d52b45e773e8404de189621ff3/d9489/image-22.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 138%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/9e4fe4d52b45e773e8404de189621ff3/d9489/image-22.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9e4fe4d52b45e773e8404de189621ff3/8a4e8/image-22.png 150w,\n/static/9e4fe4d52b45e773e8404de189621ff3/d9489/image-22.png 258w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 276px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a70e79b08b1e48ffdbffbf1191740022/f2d11/image-23.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 122%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/a70e79b08b1e48ffdbffbf1191740022/f2d11/image-23.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a70e79b08b1e48ffdbffbf1191740022/8a4e8/image-23.png 150w,\n/static/a70e79b08b1e48ffdbffbf1191740022/f2d11/image-23.png 276w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 276px) 100vw, 276px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>切り替えたらそのまま数値と透明度(今回は 0.8)を設定すればおしまいです。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>233<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>149<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>44<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0.8<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"sassで設定する一番簡単\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sass%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%95%AA%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%98\" aria-label=\"sassで設定する一番簡単 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sassで設定する※一番簡単</h2>\n<p>Hex8 桁はアルファ値を調べないといけないし、rgba はいちいちカラーコードを切り替えないといけない＆手打ちだし、手間がかかります。\n<strong>そんな問題を Sass が解決してくれます。</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#E9952C<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0.8<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Sassならばrgbaに16進数を設定しても変換してくれます。\nもちろん変数も使えます。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">$<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#E9952C<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n$<span class=\"token property\">alpha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>0.8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>$alpha<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>引数だって。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#E9952C<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>$<span class=\"token property\">alpha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>0.8<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>開発環境やプロジェクトによっては Sass が使えないこともあると思うので、その時は手間ですが通常の CSS で設定しましょう。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"2020-10-28","slug":"/444","title":"【CSS】カラーコード＋透過を１６進数(Hex8桁)とrgbaで実装","tags":["css"],"thumbnail":{"publicURL":"/static/6c1ce5baec5e42ac1a47ef7cc3a32306/image-15.png"}},"excerpt":"background と opacity を分けるとうまくいかない ここによくあるボタンのデザインがあります。  CSS を設定するために数値を見てみます。  。そして   もしもこの…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#background-%E3%81%A8-opacity-%E3%82%92%E5%88%86%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B%E3%81%A8%E3%81%86%E3%81%BE%E3%81%8F%E3%81%84%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84\">background と opacity を分けるとうまくいかない</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#16%E9%80%B2%E6%95%B0hex%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\">16進数(Hex)で設定する</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#rgba%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\">rgbaで設定する</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sass%E3%81%A7%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%95%AA%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%98\">Sassで設定する※一番簡単</a></li>\n</ul>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"うさ技術"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"658bf610-77ea-5a6c-ad78-3b340b3afc56","frontmatter__slug":"/444","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"444"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1304567263","209911134","3832698534"],"slicesMap":{}}